WaitForThread (script event)
============================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type [idThread](Thread\_(scripting)), accessible via [sys](Scripting\_basics#sys) identifier.

Description
-----------

Waits for the given thread to terminate.

Usage
-----

*[void](Data\_types#void)* waitForThread( *[float](Data\_types#float)* **threadNumber** )

Parameters
----------

[threadNumber] - id of thread to wait for.

